    </files>
    <patterns>
      <pattern name="ADR-008 filter shape (canonical)" location="projects/spaarke-datagrid-framework-r1/notes/drafts/010-authorization-filter-shape.md">Use the shape designed in task 010.</pattern>
      <pattern name="IDistributedCache pattern" location=".claude/patterns/caching/distributed-cache.md">`GetStringAsync` → if null, fetch + `SetStringAsync` with absolute expiration.</pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load Placement Justification + filter shape design from task 010.</step>
    <step order="2">Author `Models/SavedQueryDto.cs`: `record SavedQueryDto(string EntityName, string FetchXml, string LayoutXml, string Name)` + `record SavedQuerySummaryDto(Guid Id, string Name, bool IsDefault, int QueryType)`.</step>
    <step order="3">Author `Services/Dataverse/SavedQueryService.cs`: 2 methods (`GetSavedQueryAsync`, `GetSavedQueriesForEntityAsync`), both using `IDistributedCache` with `dv:savedquery:{id}` / `dv:savedqueries:{entity}` keys, 1-hour absolute expiration; cache miss → `IServiceClient.RetrieveAsync` / `RetrieveMultipleAsync` + cache set.</step>
    <step order="4">Author `Services/Dataverse/DataverseAuthorizationFilter.cs` per task 010's shape; cached-metadata-driven privilege check (entity-only for these 2 endpoints).</step>
    <step order="5">Author `Api/Dataverse/DataverseEndpoints.cs` (or `SavedQueryEndpoints.cs`) mapping the 2 endpoints to `SavedQueryService` calls; apply filter via `.AddEndpointFilter`.</step>
    <step order="6">Register `SavedQueryService` and `DataverseAuthorizationFilter` in `Program.cs` DI. Endpoint mapping unconditional per RB-T028-03/04/05/06.</step>
    <step order="7">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` — verify zero errors.</step>
    <step order="8">Run `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive` — verify no new HIGH CVEs.</step>
    <step order="9">Check publish size delta vs. baseline per ADR-029 (`dotnet publish -c Release -r linux-x64`; compare to baseline).</step>
    <step order="10">Update TASK-INDEX (011 ✅).</step>
    <step order="11">Document any deviations from task 010's design in `notes/drafts/011-deviations.md`.</step>
  </steps>

